# V2 Backlog Tracking

When the user says "let's keep this for v2", "defer to v2", "save for v2", or any
similar phrasing, append a new checkbox item to the **## Tasks** section in `docs/V2.md`.

Format each entry as:

```
- [ ] Short description of the deferred task
```

Do not remove existing items. Always append at the bottom.
